## Codex CLI Operating Mode

When running under Codex CLI (autonomous/task mode):
1. Run `bun harness:validate --phase <CURRENT_PHASE>` before starting any phase work
2. Do not chain `bun harness:advance` calls — run one advance per session, then re-dispatch
3. Before committing, run `bun harness:validate --task <TASK_ID>` to catch guardian violations early
4. Run `bun harness:compact` before ending each session
5. If any validation fails, stop and report — do not retry the advance

When running as an orchestrator-dispatched Codex child subagent:
1. Follow the provided task packet and ownership scope only
2. Do not run full-project resume/scan loops
3. Return results to orchestrator for integration and close

